data.description: Ready for town living, but with some land? This is your property. This home has 2245 square feet and 2.1625 acres. You have city amenities with a big back yard! The inside of the home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Want to have company, no problem. This home features a living room and a large family room. Tired of the cold? You don't have to walk out to your car because you'll have a two car attached garage. Once the weather is nice if you want to add a deck it got started, but you can finish it. There is also a shed outback for more storage. This home is only missing one thing, you! Set your showing today!
